data.description: Must see this cute home! Located in Beacon Village @ Mirror Lake. Beautiful 4 bedroom 3 bath home with full finished basement, nestled in the cul-de-sac with the most lovely shade trees and landscaping. Enjoy your morning coffee on the front porch and view the lovely landscaping.  The home features hard wood flooring, fireplace, open view of living room and kitchen, split bedroom plan, and much more. The driveway entrance is at the back of the home featuring a two car garage and entry into the finished basement.  The basement includes a bedroom and another large room that could be used as a bedroom with a large office area off to the side that could be converted into a walk in closet. The original laundry room is downstairs, but is also connected upstairs bedrooms. So take your pick of where you want it to be. Enjoy entertaining your family and friends on the the large deck.  Must come and see this one.
